                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> I produced a certificate of the prisoner's former conviction—(<hi rend="italic">read—convicted May</hi>, 1843, <hi rend="italic">confined three months—three weeks solitary</hi>)—the prisoner is the person.</p>
